#!/bin/sh

cd ~/faststorage/ClaudiaI/Pasha_Results/unscaled_wigs

mkdir deeptools_out

#metagene profiles
computeMatrix reference-point \
-R /home/schmidm/annotations/hg19/snRNAs/snRNA_MS.bed \
-S *_[P,I][o,n]*.bw \
--referencePoint=TES --upstream=5000 --downstream=5000 \
--averageTypeBins=sum --missingDataAsZero --binSize=10 \
--outFileName deeptools_out/PolII_snRNA_MS_TES_matrix.gz

#body values in single bin
computeMatrix scale-regions \
-R /home/schmidm/annotations/hg19/snRNAs/snRNA_MS.bed \
-S *_[P,I][o,n]*.bw \
--upstream=0 --downstream=0 \
--averageTypeBins=mean --missingDataAsZero --binSize=100 --regionBodyLength=100 \
--outFileName deeptools_out/PolII_snRNA_MS_body1bin_matrix.gz

echo "done"

heatmaps scaled values

data('RNAseq_value_heatmap_theme', package='arsRtools')
values_heatmap <- function(scaled_BGsub_df) {
  scaled_BGsub_df %>%
    filter(scaled_BGSub_ChIP > 0,
         rel_pos > -2000, rel_pos < 5000) %>%
  mutate(id = factor(id, levels=row_order)) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x=rel_pos, y=id, fill=log2(scaled_BGSub_ChIP))) +
  geom_raster(interpolate = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(.~run) +
  RNAseq_value_heatmap_theme +
  xlab(paste0('bp to ', biotype, ' ', anchor))
}
values_heatmap(internal_body_scaled_BGsub) +
  ylab('scaled to snRNA body')

ChIPseq profile plot

meta_line_plot <- function(scaled_BGsub) {
  scaled_BGsub %>%
  group_by(siRNA, main_run, run, rel_pos) %>%
  summarize(mean_value=mean(scaled_BGSub_ChIP)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  group_by(siRNA, main_run, rel_pos) %>%
  mutate(upper = max(mean_value), lower = min(mean_value), center = mean(mean_value)) %>%
ggplot(., aes(x=rel_pos, y=center, color=siRNA)) +
  geom_ribbon(aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill=siRNA), alpha=1 ) +
  facet_grid(.~main_run) +
  lineplot_theme +
  xlim(-2000,5000) +
  xlab(paste0('bp to ', biotype, ' ', anchor))
}
meta_line_plot(internal_body_scaled_BGsub)  +
  ylab('scaled to snRNA body')

Wilcoxon FDR plot

wilcox_travel_ratio <- function(scaled_BGsub) {
  scaled_BGsub %>%
    mutate(KD = ifelse(siRNA == 'siFFL', 'siFFL', 'KD')) %>%
    select(id, KD, main_run, run, rel_pos, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
    group_by(id, KD, main_run, run, rel_pos) %>%
    spread(KD, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
    group_by(main_run, rel_pos) %>%
    do(tidy(wilcox.test(.$KD, .$siFFL, alternative = 'greater', paired=T))) %>%
    group_by(main_run) %>% #alternative use fdr using all samples ie ungroup() here??
    mutate(fdr = p.adjust(p.value, method='fdr'))
}
line_plot_sigtest <- function(sigtest) {
  ggplot(sigtest, aes(x=rel_pos, y=-log10(fdr))) +
    geom_line() +
    facet_grid(.~main_run) +
  lineplot_theme +
  xlim(-2000,5000) +
    geom_hline(yintercept = 1, color='orange', linetype=2) +
  xlab(paste0('bp to ', biotype, ' ', anchor))
} 
wilcox_travel_ratio(internal_body_scaled_BGsub) %>%
line_plot_sigtest(.)

heatmaps logFC

data('RNAseq_logFC_heatmap_theme', package='arsRtools')
log_ratio <- function(scaled_BGsub) {
  min_val <- min(scaled_BGsub$scaled_BGSub_ChIP[scaled_BGsub$scaled_BGSub_ChIP>0])
  
  scaled_BGsub %>%
  mutate(KD = ifelse(siRNA == 'siFFL', 'siFFL', 'KD'),
         scaled_BGSub_ChIP = ifelse(scaled_BGSub_ChIP <= 0, min_val, scaled_BGSub_ChIP+min_val)) %>%
  dplyr::select(id, rel_pos, KD, main_run, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
  group_by(KD, id, main_run, KD, rel_pos) %>%
  summarize(scaled_BGSub_ChIP = mean(scaled_BGSub_ChIP)) %>%
  spread(KD, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
  mutate(log2_ratio = log2(KD)-log2(siFFL) )
}
internal_body_scaled_BGsub_ratio <- log_ratio(internal_body_scaled_BGsub)
heatmap_ratio <- function(scaled_ratio_df) {
  scaled_ratio_df %>%
    filter(!is.na(log2_ratio),
         rel_pos > -2000, rel_pos < 5000) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
  mutate(log2_ratio = case_when(.$log2_ratio > 2 ~ 2,
                                .$log2_ratio < -2 ~ -2,
                                TRUE ~ .$log2_ratio),
         id = factor(id, levels=row_order)) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x=rel_pos, y=id, fill=log2_ratio)) +
  geom_raster(interpolate = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(.~main_run) +
  RNAseq_logFC_heatmap_theme
}
heatmap_ratio(internal_body_scaled_BGsub_ratio)  +
  ylab('log2FC based on values scaled to snRNA body')
